      This is just the quickest way to update everyone. Ralph Marriott Ralph Marriott was in the hospital for A Fib since Tuesday, yesterday while Mom and I were there with him, he had a stroke. He was transferred from Norman to OU Med. They had him on the table in 17 minutes (they said it was their record fastest), and they were able to remove a 6mm clot. He is doing much better today. He was able to walk without the walker, and his speech is much improved. I’ll updated as we know more.
